# Ajuste para sua execucao local (VS/dotnet run) ou Docker
@ApiMedTest_HostAddress = http://localhost:8080
@contatoId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### 1) Criar contato
POST {{ApiMedTest_HostAddress}}/api/contatos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomeContato": "Maria Oliveira",
  "dataNascimento": "1990-01-10",
  "sexo": "Feminino"
}

### 2) Listar contatos ativos
GET {{ApiMedTest_HostAddress}}/api/contatos
Accept: application/json

### 3) Buscar contato ativo por id
GET {{ApiMedTest_HostAddress}}/api/contatos/{{contatoId}}
Accept: application/json

### 4) Atualizar contato ativo
PUT {{ApiMedTest_HostAddress}}/api/contatos/{{contatoId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomeContato": "Maria Oliveira Souza",
  "dataNascimento": "1990-01-10",
  "sexo": "Feminino"
}

### 5) Desativar contato
PATCH {{ApiMedTest_HostAddress}}/api/contatos/{{contatoId}}/desativar
Accept: application/json

### 6) Ativar contato
PATCH {{ApiMedTest_HostAddress}}/api/contatos/{{contatoId}}/ativar
Accept: application/json

### 7) Excluir contato
DELETE {{ApiMedTest_HostAddress}}/api/contatos/{{contatoId}}
Accept: application/json
